Alumni Europae ASBL - We are Alumni Europae ASBL, the association for former students of the European Schools. We're a non-profit organisation that solidifies the expansive network of current and former European School (ES) students by providing a platform for communication and laying the foundations for the network's future expansion and diversification. Join us and keep us to date with whats going on in your community!
